author: erodriguez
msg: Changes to server-main's server.xml for testing:
o  Enabled Kerberos and Change Password protocols.
o  Enabled all encryption types:  aes256-cts-hmac-sha1-96 aes128-cts-hmac-sha1-96 des3-cbc-sha1-kd des-cbc-md5
o  Disabled Kerberos-aware LDIF filter since it conflicts with the KeyDerivationService interceptor.

author: jsdelfino
msg: Cleaned up host-embedded, removed unused classes. Added a bean variant of SCADomain for use in environments where a bean is more convenient that a factory with newInstance.
